'''Mielps''' were a group that inhabited [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]]. During a crisis in which the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Ansion/Legends|Ansion]] threatened to secede from the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]], at least three Mielps were present in the Ansionian [[City/Legends|city]] of [[Cuipernam]]. Traveling through a Cuipernan marketplace carrying shopping bags nearly matching their own size, they forced [[Jedi Master/Legends|Jedi Master]] [[Luminara Unduli/Legends|Luminara Unduli]] to move to avoid them during her [[Border dispute on Ansion/Legends|mission to Ansion]]<ref name="Storm">''[[The Approaching Storm]]''</ref> in [[22 BBY/Legends|22 BBY]].<ref name="Date">''[[The Essential Reader's Companion]]''</ref>

==Behind the scenes==
Mielps appeared in the novel ''[[The Approaching Storm]]'', written by [[Alan Dean Foster]] and published in [[2002]].<ref name="Storm" />

